  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK488">
<l>ceṟunaraik kāṇiṟ cumakka viṟuvarai</l>
<l>kāṇiṟ kiḻakkān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one meets his enemy, let him show him all respect, until the time for his destruction is come; when that is come, his head will be easily brought low.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
